{"tid":1356123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係度屌失焦嘅各位入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:18:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:06:02.000Z","uid":103960,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"87e93e80de615e34b832ad51df15c0b46364f4ff","tid":1356123,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:18:56.000Z","msg":"我明白大家好關心中左槍嘅手足<br />\n同埋驚大家忘記咗最初嘅訴求<br />\n大家都開始急 所以會開始屌自己人 <br />\n但希望大家可以靜心睇完<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 屯天元嘅手足真係好需要大家</strong><br />\n今次元朗鄉黑襲擊呢件事，其實對住屯天元嘅手足影響都好大，唔係話驚，而係真係會有危險<br />\n你地有無諗過佢地次次都過海咁出港島奮戰，夜晚到底點返屋企？<br />\n可能係坐通宵小巴、的士，或者有Ｄ人會早少少走而坐尾班西鐵，但你有無諗過屯天元咁大，佢地落咗車可能仲要行一大段路先返到屋企？<br />\n佢地嘅安危唔通唔緊要咩？所以求吓大家唔好再叫人唔好去元朗<br />\n越逃避、越縱容，只會越猖狂，<br />\n我求吓大家唔好放棄屯天元。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 大家只係需要發洩，絕無忘記最初嘅訴求</strong><br />\n好多人或者會覺得何妖單嘢唔係主線，唔應該討論咁多，應該集中焦點。<br />\n係！呢樣係絕對無錯，但運動自6.9以黎，政府都無絲毫回應我地嘅訴求<br />\n雖然大家表面上無任何氣餒，但其實好多人私底下都好絕望<br />\n呢件事算唔上係勝利，但真係可以沖喜吓，振奮士氣。<br />\n但咁唔代表大家會鬆懈，<br />\n我相信大家唔會忘記最初嘅訴求，亦都唔會忘記721中槍嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 我地嘅資本只有團結　唔好再互屌</strong><br />\n我希望大家回憶起雨傘革命嘅教訓，<br />\n我地當初點解會失敗？就係互屌開始。<br />\n由互屌到割蔗，最後大家心灰意冷、泯然眾人，運動以失敗告吹。<br />\n大家記住，我地走到今日可以攻陷立法會，包圍中聯辦，只係憑藉我地嘅<strong>團結</strong>同<strong>勇氣</strong><br />\n<br />\n到最後，我都明好多屌失焦嘅手足係想大家關注當日係港島被槍傷嘅手足<br />\n我會盡力幫大家推ｐｏ<br />\n求下大家唔好再互屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"863bc93b3acf12ad8ffa17dc4c83d0462c8b9cdb","tid":1356123,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:19:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfcac6a7237ac72809e191ae24a5674acc7d1157","tid":1356123,"uid":126420,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:19:22.000Z","msg":"PUSH，係元朗聚焦返 5 大訴求<br />\n1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 撤銷6.12暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4. 全面實行雙普選<br />\n5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲"},{"pid":"b4eb63c37a1e926bb01e978e8bfabf6c6317ff67","tid":1356123,"uid":226819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:19:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94456de696aa168de24fba3a459e3416feeeb700","tid":1356123,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5286790bc971be4dfb914894329532a6d15496c3","tid":1356123,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:21:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"e94db2c9e3e56f63020f36978a958b25d8d35c57","tid":1356123,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:22:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bcf17af4d5647565eea1de28c81a0e1c6d72261","tid":1356123,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:23:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5723bb5004e7a1121360b3fb00c1dc219f8e5ed6","tid":1356123,"uid":103960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:25:19.000Z","msg":"希望大家都幫手推返開槍單野上熱門<br />\n然後727一齊出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ba71f869c03d070c21cdb1e1d2b7c1da35c165","tid":1356123,"uid":156632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:25:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家唔好要義士白白犧牲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"93fd52a175a57247903cd8e3f30338975c515034","tid":1356123,"uid":34415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:26:57.000Z","msg":"新西人表示次次咁撚遠都出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊光復元朗 一齊反恐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26c3d4da3008154ea592719e57328175eb75871e","tid":1356123,"uid":210691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1a6d8690b37e4e86c0d5f35786f48436eabe3f","tid":1356123,"uid":195887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bvnc3LQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvnc3LQ.png&h=b85e599c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二層都滿足唔到，仲講民主自由？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8291dfb6a0b2980e96e88f5b4ee8c471822bd501","tid":1356123,"uid":103960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e1a6d8690b37e4e86c0d5f35786f48436eabe3f","tid":1356123,"uid":195887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bvnc3LQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvnc3LQ.png&h=b85e599c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二層都滿足唔到，仲講民主自由？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係<br />\n到時有雙普選都無用<br />\n成班黑社會企係票站幫你投票"},{"pid":"26dd7d557f9bd708b97ac1b67736d757491dc79a","tid":1356123,"uid":11066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，警黑合作，一齊去一齊返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不互屌 不割蓆"},{"pid":"ca65bc90031219c538ad2187f4801cd5507390d3","tid":1356123,"uid":103960,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"26dd7d557f9bd708b97ac1b67736d757491dc79a","tid":1356123,"uid":11066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:46:51.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，警黑合作，一齊去一齊返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不互屌 不割蓆"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:59:33.000Z","msg":